When I did my '59 Kombi, I mounted some of the enclosed speakers under my 
parcel tray. Worked real good and only made one small hole in the try for 
each speaker. They look like you'd hit your knees on 'em...but in reality 
they didn't even come close to getting in the way. Here's some pictures at 
the bottom of this page:
http://www.type2guy.com/59/59extra2.html



